results.title: Live more, Worry Less Sticker - Car, Cup or Crafts Decal - Choose your Color
results.description:
Easily apply this decal to your favorite coffee mug, any vehicle, your front door, a storefront window, tool box, skateboard, a kayak, your dogs water bowl and every thing in between. Any hard surface that is mostly flat will do. They are weather resistant, waterproof and last up to 6 years outdoors. Each decal is made to order and can be customized to your liking. Be sure to shoot me a message beforehand to inquire about any extra fees. All packages come with precise, easy to follow instructions. Orders are made and shipped within 48 hours excluding holidays and weekends. 

Want to see more? www.etsy.com/shop/designsbytrb

USPS First Class Shipping is included! You will have the option to upgrade your shipping upon checkout. Please scroll down to the PRODUCTION AND SHIPPING section to read more.

*No frill packaging, just the goods* :)

PRODUCT INFORMATION:
These are not printed, they are hand weeded. I use top quality adhesive vinyl with a paper backing that protects the decal until removed. It has a permanent adhesive that is great for outdoor use for 3-6 years. By default, these decals are meant to be put on the OUTSIDE of a window. If you need it reversed (for inside of a window or jewelry) please leave me a note! This vinyl can be used indoors but be weary of it pulling up paint. Let me know if you plan to use your decal on a painted wall and I will use a more suitable vinyl.

COLOR OPTIONS:

Please select the color that you would like your design to be made with from the drop down menu. I cannot bulk edit the options so you may encounter a listing without the option you would like. In this case, simply type the color into the notes portion. You can view the colors available in the listing photos. Red - Orange - Yellow - Coral or Peach - Hot Pink - Soft Pink - Lime Green - Mint - Ice blue - Pale Tiffany Blue - Lilac or Light Purple - Silver - Rose Gold - White - Black

DIRECTIONS FOR APPLICATION:
Easy to apply! Clean the desired area thoroughly. Avoid any window cleaners before application. Peel off paper backing and smooth onto the location. Use a card to smooth out any bubbles. When you're done, don't forget to remove the transfer tape! Please look over the email you receive for further instructions. You may also find directions in the FAQ

PRODUCTION AND SHIPPING:
Each decal is made to order. Please allow up to 3 business days for your order to be created.
The free option will be sent in either a white letter envelope with a printed stamp or a manila envelope with printed postage. 

Orders are made and shipped in the order they are received unless you choose the "skip the line" option. This upgrade puts your order to the very top of my list and will be the first order to ship Monday thru Friday. Skip the line orders will still be shipped via First Class Mail and include basic tracking.

Additionally, you can upgrade to Priority Mail 3-Day. Priority Mail will go through the postal system quicker but is not guaranteed to arrive in 3 days. This option includes more in-depth tracking. Please visit the usps official website for more information on their Covid19/Election time restrictions and delays. 
No frill packaging!
CUSTOMIZATION:
Certain decals require a little customization. If your order requires names, dates or a website link, please leave that information in the Notes to Seller portion upon check out. I will contact you if I need any further information. Please occasionally check your spam folder in the event that my email has been directed there. *Be sure to double check everything before you submit it.*

PROMOTION AND SPECIALS: 
You can view any current or upcoming promotions on the Shop Announcement located at the top of my shop. A link to the front page is at the bottom of this description.
